 16   Psyche               9.6
 349  Dembowska            9.7
 12   Victoria             9.7
 44   Nysa                 9.7
 192  Nausikaa             9.8
 13   Egeria               9.8
 19   Fortuna              9.9
 5    Astraea              9.9
 51   Nemausa              9.9
 230  Athamantis           9.9
 354  Eleonora             9.9
 704  Interamnia          10.0
 43   Ariadne             10.0
 21   Lutetia             10.1
 115  Thyra               10.1
 324  Bamberga            10.1
 23   Thalia              10.1
 30   Urania              10.1
 63   Ausonia             10.2
 22   Kalliope            10.2
 68   Leto                10.3
 42   Isis                10.3
 433  Eros                10.3
 4544 Xanthus             10.3
 80   Sappho              10.3
 52   Europa              10.4
 511  Davida              10.4
